  "title": "Luxury Watch Protection Film Installer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Watchskins Pte Ltd</strong> (operating as Watchskins Singapore) is a\nspecialised luxury watch protective film and care service provider. We also provide complimentary services\nsuch as accuracy testing, water resistance checks, and steam cleaning to ensure holistic care for every timepiece.<br /></p><p><strong>Your jobscope</strong></p><p>·   Apply precision-cut protective films to luxury watches, ensuring a flawless, bubble-free finish</p><p>·   Customize and trim films to fit different watch models and brands</p><p>·   Handle high-value timepieces with care and expertise</p><p>·   Maintain tools and workstations for optimal efficiency</p><p>·   Support the team in achieving store sales targets and customer satisfaction goals.</p><p><strong>We’re Looking For</strong></p><p>· Experience in <strong>film application, watch handling, manicure or related fields</strong>\n(preferred but not required)</p><p>· Keen eye for detail and steady hands for precision work</p><p>· Passion for luxury watches and high-end craftsmanship</p><p>· Good communication skills for customer interaction</p><p>·  Able to communicate effectively in English with customers</p><p>·  Willingness to learn and master new techniques</p><p>·  Able to work retail hours, including weekends and public holidays.<br /></p><p></p>",
